file.name: passwordutility.net-v1-swagger.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.0
info:
  description: Validate and generate passwords using open source tools
  title: PasswordUtility.Web
  version: v1
  x-apisguru-categories:
    - security
    - tools
  x-origin:
    - format: swagger
      url: http://passwordutility.net/swagger/docs/v1
      version: "2.0"
  x-providerName: passwordutility.net
paths:
  /api/password/generate:
    post:
      deprecated: false
      operationId: Password_Generate
      parameters:
        - in: query
          name: length
          required: true
          schema:
            type: integer
            format: int32
        - in: query
          name: upperCase
          required: false
          schema:
            type: boolean
        - in: query
          name: digits
          required: false
          schema:
            type: boolean
        - in: query
          name: specialCharacters
          required: false
          schema:
            type: boolean
      responses:
        "200":
          description: OK
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: "#/components/schemas/Object"
            text/json:
              schema:
                $ref: "#/components/schemas/Object"
            application/xml:
              schema:
                $ref: "#/components/schemas/Object"
            text/xml:
              schema:
                $ref: "#/components/schemas/Object"
      tags:
        - Password
  /api/password/validate:
    post:
      deprecated: false
      operationId: Password_Validate
      parameters:
        - in: query
          name: password
          required: true
          schema:
            type: string
      responses:
        "200":
          description: OK
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: "#/components/schemas/Object"
            text/json:
              schema:
                $ref: "#/components/schemas/Object"
            application/xml:
              schema:
                $ref: "#/components/schemas/Object"
            text/xml:
              schema:
                $ref: "#/components/schemas/Object"
      tags:
        - Password
servers:
  - url: http://passwordutility.net:80
components:
  schemas:
    Object:
      properties: {}
      type: object
